    "body": "For anyone else coming across this a year later. Adding this to `~/.bashrc` solved it for me:\n```bash\n# Clear old Starship hooks to prevent infinite loops when sourcing\nunset -f starship_precmd\nif [[ \"$PROMPT_COMMAND\" == *starship_precmd* ]]; then\n    PROMPT_COMMAND=\"${PROMPT_COMMAND//starship_precmd/}\"\nfi\n\n# Now initialize safely\neval \"$(starship init bash)\"\n```",
